_sText:
From the map MOTD:

The long awaited func_vehicle shipment has 
just arrived at the Crazytank HQ.  Only someone 
has jammed gum in the receiving doors so we 
cannot unload the precious cargo and thus 
cannot install it into the crazytank.  

Terrorists have gotten word of this folly and 
are using it as a time to step up their attack 
on the crazytank HQ.  They will either blow 
up the func_vehicle container or the crazytank 
itself.

Curse the person who jammed gum in the locks!  
What kind of madman wouldnâ€™t want func_vehicle 
in Counter-Strike: Source?
